item.title: [508]How to change home and the place home teleport teles you?
item.dc:creator: @arham_4 arham 4
item.description:
@arham_4 wrote:

Well, found this really cool never before seen place for home, and I thought I should use it. How do I change home? Also, I found my home teleport, it goes by city to home, not by coords, and my place is under the chaos druids hideout. Heresthe home tele code:

                    case 16: // Home teleport
                        if (p.teleblocked) {
                            p.getActionSender().sendMessage(p, "You are teleport blocked!");
                            return;
                        }
                        p.cityTeleport("Edgeville");
                        break;

Thanks,
Arham
